label: Fiscal County
desc: County of fiscal responsibility, which is typically the county of recipient’s residence

label: Service Category
desc: Individual Medicaid chemical dependent service categories. Note: This may also include an indication of: All Medicaid Services, All Alcohol and Substance Abuse (ASA) Services, All Non-ASA Services

label: Unique Enrollees
desc: Number of unique Medicaid enrollees for whom a claim was paid for a type of service received during the SFY*

label: Service Units
desc: The number of service units (e.g. days, visits, weeks) for which Medicaid paid during a SFY*

label: Avg Payment per Recipient
desc: The dollar amount paid by Medicaid for services rendered divided by the number of recipients who received services during the SFY*

label: Avg Payment per Claim
desc: The dollar amount paid by Medicaid for services rendered divided by the number of claims submitted during the SFY*

label: Total Payment
desc: The dollar amount paid by Medicaid for services rendered during the SFY * based on date of service

label: State Fiscal Year
desc: 4-digit State Fiscal Year, which runs from April 1st through March 31st. For example, the SFY for 2017 would occur between April 1, 2016 and March 31, 2017. Beginning with SFY 2016-2017, Medicaid billing includes both Fee for Service (FFS) and Managed Care (MC). Totals for each billing source are represented in the data beginning with SFY 2017.

label: Service Indicators
desc: Summary indicators for separate chemical dependence service categories as well as indicators for All Medicaid Services, All Alcohol and Substance Abuse (ASA) and All Non-ASA Services

label: Unique Enrollees FFS
desc: The number of unique Medicaid enrollees for whom a claim was paid for a type of service received during the state fiscal year

label: FFS Service Units
desc: The number of service units (e.g. days, visits, weeks) for which Medicaid Fee-for-Service (FFS) paid during a state fiscal year

label: FFS Total Payment
desc: The dollar amount paid by Medicaid FFS for services rendered during the state fiscal year based on date of service

label: State Fiscal Year FFS
desc: 4-digit State Fiscal Year (SFY), which runs from April 1st through March 31st. For example, the SFY for 2003 would occur between April 1, 2002 and March 31, 2003.
